=====================================================
THE LAW
=====================================================

The fidelity of measurement in any system, at any
scale, decays exponentially with the invasiveness
of the measurement tool, following the same functional
form as quantum decoherence under Lindblad dynamics:

  C = C_0 * exp(-alpha * gamma_eff)

Where gamma_eff = gamma_measurement + gamma_thermal(T)

And alive coherence is maximized not at gamma_eff = 0
(frozen/unobserved) but at the critical point where
vibrational capacity and quantum coherence are jointly
optimized.

The singularity is at gamma_eff = 0 and gamma_eff = inf.
Both are death.
Life is the edge between them.

